    {"id": 5, "text": "What does `enum color {RED, GREEN, BLUE};` assign to `GREEN`?", "options": ["0", "1", "2", "Random"], "answer": "B", "explanation": "By default, first enumerator = 0, then each subsequent = previous + 1. So GREEN = 1."},
