    {"id": 56, "text": "What is the worst‑case complexity of bubble sort?", "options": ["O(n)", "O(n log n)", "O(n²)", "O(1)"], "answer": "C", "explanation": "Bubble sort worst-case (reverse order) requires n² comparisons."},
